<h2 id="with-μ‹λ¦¬μ¦"><span style="color:navy">with μ‹λ¦¬μ¦<span></span></span></h2>

<p>λ°μ΄ν„°ν”„λ μ„μ€ μ‹λ¦¬μ¦μ™€λ„ μ—°μ‚°μ„ μν–‰ν•  μ μλ‹¤. <u>λ°μ΄ν„°ν”„λ μ„μ  ν–‰(axis=1)μ¶•μ„ κΈ°μ¤€μΌλ΅ λ¨λ“  ν–‰μ μ—΄ μ΄λ¦„κ³Ό μ‹λ¦¬μ¦μ μΈλ±μ¤ μ΄λ¦„μ΄ λ™μΌν• μ„μΉμΈ μ›μ†λΌλ¦¬ κ³„μ‚°</u>λμ–΄μ§„λ‹¤.  λ”λ¶μ–΄, λ‹¤λ¥Έ κ³„μ‚°λ“¤κ³Ό λ§μ°¬κ°€μ§€λ΅ μ§μ΄ μ—†μ„ κ²½μ° <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">NaN</code>μΌλ΅ μ²λ¦¬λμ–΄μ§€λ©°, λ°ν™λ κ²°κ³Όλ΅ λ°μ΄ν„°ν”„λ μ„μ— μ—†λ μ—΄μ΄ μ¶”κ°€λμ–΄ λ°μ΄ν„°ν”„λ μ„ κ°μ²΄λ΅ λ°ν™λμ–΄μ§„λ‹¤.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">df</span> <span class="o">=</span> \
<span class="n">pd</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="s">'c0'</span><span class="p">:[</span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">20</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">30</span><span class="p">],</span> 
